    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable daily driver, and it's been such a fantastic car for me. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been super well-maintained\u2014honestly, it still drives like a dream! If you're looking for a dependable ride that's ready for your next road trip or just the daily commute, this is the one. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so come by and check it out!",
