    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking reliability and style. The exterior retains a beautiful luster, showing only minor signs of careful use consistent with its history. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean, with well-preserved upholstery and all electronic features functioning exactly as they should. Under the hood, it has been serviced regularly, resulting in a smooth, quiet ride and responsive handling. It drives beautifully and has clearly been a pride of ownership. This is a solid, well-maintained car that balances performance and comfort perfectly, ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
