    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolute gold to me. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014runs like a dream and has been super well-maintained over the years. It's been my reliable daily driver and still looks fantastic on the road. I'm looking for a new home for it where it'll be just as appreciated. Come take it for a spin, you're going to love how it handles!",
